ty</strong></h3>\r\nEthics and honorable business practices are truly important to us at Totally Tent and Party Rental. One of our fundamental values is that we will not \"nickel and dime\" our customers through hidden fees or charges. Our prices are straightforward and clearly stated. Our goal is always to match our customers needs and budget with the appropriate products.</li>\r\n\r\n<br>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<li><h3><strong>Competitive Pricing</strong></h3>\r\nWe price our products in a way that gives our customers the most for their money. Our philosophy can be seen in all of our pricing practices.</li>\r\n\r\n<br>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<li><h3><strong>Quality Products</strong></h3>\r\nOur Company uses the highest quality products in the industry. The products we rent out are clean, durable, and attractive.</li>\r\n\r\n<br>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<li><h3><strong>Punctual, Professional Service</strong></h3>\r\nA major priority for our company is to deliver our products in a timely fashion, preferably well in advance, to give our customers peace of mind and make event preparations as smooth as possible. Our staff is well trained, polite and efficient.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Values','','inherit','closed','closed','','325-revision-v1','','','2016-03-10 18:17:16','2016-03-10 18:17:16','',325,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/2016/03/10/325-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(344,2,'2016-03-10 18:18:09','2016-03-10 18:18:09','<h2>Community Involvement</h2>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px;\">\r\nWe are a community oriented organization that believes it is essential to be actively engaged in activities that benefit the lives of individuals and worthy causes in our area. Our official charity since our inception in 2004 has been the Dream Factory for chronically or terminally ill children. Their mission is \"The Dream Factory grants dreams to children diagnosed with critical or chronic illnesses who are 3 through 18 years of age.\" We also support <a href=\"http://www.easterseals.com/newyork/\" target=\"_blank\">Easter Seals Disability Services</a> whose mission is to \"provide exceptional services, education, outreach, and advocacy so that people living with autism and other disabilities can live, learn, work and play in our communities.\"\r\n</div>','Community','','inherit','closed','closed','','332-revision-v1','','','2016-03-10 18:18:09','2016-03-10 18:18:09','',332,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/2016/03/10/332-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(347,2,'2016-03-10 18:21:12','2016-03-10 18:21:12',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','347','','','2016-04-16 01:15:09','2016-04-16 01:15:09','',301,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/?p=347',20,'nav_menu_item','',0),(348,2,'2016-03-10 18:21:12','2016-03-10 18:21:12',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','348','','','2016-04-16 01:15:09','2016-04-16 01:15:09','',301,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/?p=348',19,'nav_menu_item','',0),(349,2,'2016-03-10 18:50:34','2016-03-10 18:50:34','<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 20px;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Where is Totally Tent and Party Rental located?</strong>\r\n<em>Totally Tent and Party Rental has recently moved! Our new warehouse facility is located at:\r\n\r\n2438 Union Street\r\nBuilding 2, Suite C\r\nSpencerport, NY 14559</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>How many years have you been in business?</strong>\r\n<em>Totally Tent and Party Rental, Inc. has been proudly serving Rochester and the surrounding communities for 14 years. We have had the privilege of serving over 3,000 customers. Totally Tent and Party Rental is proud to be the only accredited member of the Better Business Bureau in our industry in the Rochester area.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Do you deliver?</strong>\r\n<em>Yes, all tent rentals are delivered and installed by a member of Totally Tent and Party Rental\'s highly trained staff.\r\n\r\nClients who wish to rent tables and chairs only can pick these items up at our work facility or have them delivered by our staff. Table and chair deliveries have a round trip delivery fee applied to them.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What are your delivery fees and areas?</strong>\r\n<em>We have a detailed breakdown on delivery rates by location found here.</em</li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Do I need to sign a rental agreement?</strong>\r\n<em>Yes, all customers renting products from Totally Tent and Party Rental, will be sent a written rental contract that will document the terms and conditions of our services. This document must be signed and returned with a deposit to confirm a reservation.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What are your rental periods?</strong>\r\n<em>Inflatable Rentals: Half day rentals 4 hours, Full day rental 8 hours. \r\n*Inflatables CANNOT be used in adverse weather conditions. Adverse weather can be cause for cancellation. Please refer to our weather conditions and safety link.\r\n\r\nConcession Equipment (Popcorn, Sno Kone and Cotton Candy Machines): \r\n1 day rental\r\n\r\nTent Rentals:\r\nSmaller than 30 x 60: 1 day rental\r\n30 x 60 or larger: 2 day rental\r\nTable and Chairs: 1 day rental</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What to expect upon table and chair delivery?</strong>\r\n<em>Upon delivery, all tables and chairs will be unloaded and stacked in close proximity from the point of arrival. Our staff should not be expected to manually transport items unreasonable distances from our arrival location. If tables and chairs must be carried long distances or up several flights of stairs, additional fees will be applied.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What to expect upon tent delivery?</strong>\r\n<em>Your tent will be installed by our courteous and highly trained staff. If tables and chairs accompany your order, they will be stacked neatly underneath the tent.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What to expect upon pickup?</strong>\r\n<em>All rental items should be accounted for and stacked neatly in close proximity to the location where the rental items were setup or dropped off. If any rental items are damaged or lost, replacement fees will be accessed in accordance with our rental contract.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>If I rent a tent, does the rental price include installation and takedown?</strong>\r\n<em>Yes, setup and takedown is included in all tent rental prices. The installation and takedown of tents is performed by the highly trained staff of Totally Tent and Party Rental.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What are your deposit guidelines?</strong>\r\n<em>We require a deposit in the amount of one third of the total amount due. We request that your deposit is made by credit card in order to confirm your reservation in a timely fashion. We accept Visa, Discover and Master Card.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>When do you require payment?</strong>\r\n<em>After a deposit is made, final payment is due upon our arrival at your event location. Accepted forms of final payment are credit card, cash, check or money order.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Is final credit card payment accepted and processed by installation staff upon their arrival at my event?</strong>\r\n<em>If you wish to make your final payment by credit card, you must contact the Totally Tent and Party Rental office staff. Our installation staff does not have the authority to accept or process credit cards. Totally Tent and Party Rental accepts Visa, Discover and Master Card.</emm></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Who should checks or money orders be made out to?</strong></li>\r\n<em>All checks and money orders should be made payable to Totally Tent and Party Rental.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>What is your cancellation policy?</strong>\r\n<em>In the case of a cancellation, we credit our customer\'s existing account in the amount of their deposit. This credit can be used at any time and will not have an expiration date. The use of credits and the rescheduling of events is dependent on product availability. Customer credits are not transferable to other individuals. Totally Tent and Party Rental does not give monetary refunds.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>How soon before my event will the tent be setup?</strong></li>\r\n<em>Typically, tent installations are done 1-2 days prior to the date of your event.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>How should I prepare for the arrival of the tent?</strong>\r\n<em>We request that the person who placed the order is present at the event location upon our staff\'s arrival, so they can indicate exactly where the tent should be installed.</li>\r\n\r\nWe request that all lawn maintenance (mowing) is completed prior to our arrival. For customers with Saturday events, all lawn care should be completed by the Wednesday prior to your event. This will prevent any conflict with our standard tent installation schedule.\r\n\r\nTotally Tent and Party Rental does not give monetary refunds under any circumstances.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','FAQ','','publish','closed','closed','','faq','','','2016-04-07 19:24:30','2016-04-07 19:24:30','',0,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/?page_id=349',0,'page','',0),(350,2,'2016-03-10 18:30:01','2016-03-10 18:30:01','<ul>\r\n<li>Where is Totally Tent and Party Rental located?\r\nAnswer: Totally Tent and Party Rental has recently moved! Our new warehouse facility is located at:\r\n\r\n2438 Union Street\r\nBuilding 2, Suite C\r\nSpencerport, NY 14559</li>\r\n\r\n<li>How many years have you been in business?\r\nAnswer: Totally Tent and Party Rental, Inc. has been proudly serving Rochester and the surrounding communities for 14 years. We have had the privilege of serving over 3,000 customers. Totally Tent and Party Rental is proud to be the only accredited member of the Better Business Bureau in our industry in the Rochester area.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Do you deliver?\r\nAnswer: Yes, all tent rentals are delivered and installed by a member of Totally Tent and Party Rental\'s highly trained staff.\r\n\r\nClients who wish to rent tables and chairs only can pick these items up at our work facility or have them delivered by our staff. Table and chair deliveries have a round trip delivery fee applied to them.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What are your delivery fees and areas?\r\nAnswer: We have a detailed breakdown on delivery rates by location found <a href=\"../delivery-rates/\">here</a></li>\r\n\r\n<li>Do I need to sign a rental agreement?\r\nAnswer: Yes, all customers renting products from Totally Tent and Party Rental, will be sent a written rental contract that will document the terms and conditions of our services. This document must be signed and returned with a deposit to confirm a reservation.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What are your rental periods?\r\nAnswer: Inflatable Rentals: Half day rentals 4 hours, Full day rental 8 hours. \r\n*Inflatables CANNOT be used in adverse weather conditions. Adverse weather can be cause for cancellation. Please refer to our weather conditions and safety link.\r\n\r\nConcession Equipment (Popcorn, Sno Kone and Cotton Candy Machines): 1 day rental\r\n\r\nTent Rentals:\r\nSmaller than 30 x 60: 1 day rental\r\n30 x 60 or larger: 2 day rental\r\nTable and Chairs: 1 day rental</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What to expect upon table and chair delivery?\r\nAnswer: Upon delivery, all tables and chairs will be unloaded and stacked in close proximity from the point of arrival. Our staff should not be expected to manually transport items unreasonable distances from our arrival location. If tables and chairs must be carried long distances or up several flights of stairs, additional fees will be applied.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What to expect upon tent delivery?\r\nAnswer: Your tent will be installed by our courteous and highly trained staff. If tables and chairs accompany your order, they will be stacked neatly underneath the tent.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What to expect upon pickup?\r\nAnswer: All rental items should be accounted for and stacked neatly in close proximity to the location where the rental items were setup or dropped off. If any rental items are damaged or lost, replacement fees will be accessed in accordance with our rental contract.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>If I rent a tent, does the rental price include installation and takedown?\r\nAnswer: Yes, setup and takedown is included in all tent rental prices. The installation and takedown of tents is performed by the highly trained staff of Totally Tent and Party Rental.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What are your deposit guidelines?\r\nAnswer: We require a deposit in the amount of one third of the total amount due. We request that your deposit is made by credit card in order to confirm your reservation in a timely fashion. We accept Visa, Discover and Master Card.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>When do you require payment?\r\nAnswer: After a deposit is made, final payment is due upon our arrival at your event location. Accepted forms of final payment are credit card, cash, check or money order.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Is final credit card payment accepted and processed by installation staff upon their arrival at my event?\r\nAnswer: If you wish to make your final payment by credit card, you must contact the Totally Tent and Party Rental office staff. Our installation staff does not have the authority to accept or process credit cards. Totally Tent and Party Rental accepts Visa, Discover and Master Card.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Who should checks or money orders be made out to?\r\nAnswer: All checks and money orders should be made payable to Totally Tent and Party Rental.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>What is your cancellation policy?\r\nAnswer: In the case of a cancellation, we credit our customer\'s existing account in the amount of their deposit. This credit can be used at any time and will not have an expiration date. The use of credits and the rescheduling of events is dependent on product availability. Customer credits are not transferable to other individuals. Totally Tent and Party Rental does not give monetary refunds.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>How soon before my event will the tent be setup?\r\nAnswer: Typically, tent installations are done 1-2 days prior to the date of your event.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>How should I prepare for the arrival of the tent?\r\nAnswer: We request that the person who placed the order is present at the event location upon our staff\'s arrival, so they can indicate exactly where the tent should be installed.</li>\r\n\r\nWe request that all lawn maintenance (mowing) is completed prior to our arrival. For customers with Saturday events, all lawn care should be completed by the Wednesday prior to your event. This will prevent any conflict with our standard tent installation schedule.\r\n\r\nTotally Tent and Party Rental does not give monetary refunds under any circumstances.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n','FAQ','','inherit','closed','closed','','349-revision-v1','','','2016-03-10 18:30:01','2016-03-10 18:30:01','',349,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/2016/03/10/349-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(351,2,'2016-03-10 18:31:01','2016-03-10 18:31:01','<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 20px; font-size; 20px; line-height: 30px;>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Where is Totally Tent and Party Rental located?\r\nAnswer: Totally Tent and Party Rental has recently moved! Our new warehouse facility is located at:\r\n\r\n2438 Union Street\r\nBuilding 2, Suite C\r\nSpencerport, NY 14559</li>\r\n\r\n<li>How many years have you been in business?\r\nAnswer: Totally Tent and Party Rental, Inc. has been proudly serving Rochester and the surrounding communities for 14 years. We have had the privilege of serving over 3,000 customers. Totally Tent and Party Rental is proud to be the only accredited member of the Better Business Bureau in our industry in the Rochester area.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Do you deliver?\r\nAnswer: Yes, all tent rentals are delivered and installed by a member of Totally Tent and Party Rental\'s highly trained staff.\r\n\r\nCl