accordance with our rental contract.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><h3><strong>If I rent a tent, does the rental price include installation and takedown?</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Yes, setup and takedown is included in all tent rental prices. The installation and takedown of tents is performed by the highly trained staff of Totally Tent and Party Rental.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><h3><strong>What are your deposit guidelines?</strong></h3>\r\n<em>We require a deposit in the amount of one third of the total amount due. We request that your deposit is made by credit card in order to confirm your reservation in a timely fashion. We accept Visa, Discover and Master Card.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><h3><strong>When do you require payment?</strong></h3>\r\n<em>After a deposit is made, final payment is due upon our arrival at your event location. Accepted forms of final payment are credit card, cash, check or money order.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><h3><strong>Is final credit card payment accepted and processed by installation staff upon their arrival at my event?</strong></h3>\r\n<em>If you wish to make your final payment by credit card, you must contact the Totally Tent and Party Rental office staff. Our installation staff does not have the authority to accept or process credit cards. Totally Tent and Party Rental accepts Visa, Discover and Master Card.</emm></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><h3><strong>Who should checks or money orders be made out to?</strong></li>\r\n<em>All checks and money orders should be made payable to Totally Tent and Party Rental.</em></li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><h3><strong>What is your cancellation policy?</strong></h3>\r\n<em>In the case of a cancellation, we credit our customer\'s existing account in the amount of their deposit. This credit can be used at any time and will not have an expiration date. The use of credits and the rescheduling of events is dependent on product availability. Customer credits are not transferable to other individuals. Totally Tent and Party Rental d