nse and adult supervision is important. A responsible adult should be monitoring the inflatable and the individual\'s inside of it at all times.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>It is Totally Tent and Party Rental\'s policy not to set up any inflatables on concrete.</li>\r\n</ol>','Inflatable Rules','','inherit','closed','closed','','554-revision-v1','','','2016-04-07 18:54:06','2016-04-07 18:54:06','',554,'http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/2016/04/07/554-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(528,2,'2016-04-05 03:47:09','2016-04-05 03:47:09','<div style=\"width: 100%; height: 340px; display: inline-block; border-top: 15px #2c3959 double;\">\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width: 8%; float: left; text-align: center;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/facebook.png\" style=\"width: 45px; height: auto; margin-top: 27px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/google.png\" style=\"width: 45px; height: auto; margin-top: 5px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/twitter.png\" style=\"width: 45px; height: auto; margin-top: 5px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/pinterest.png\" style=\"width: 45px; height: auto; margin-top: 5px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/instagram.png\" style=\"width: 45px; height: auto; margin-top: 5px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://ttents-sample.atwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/youtube.png\" style=\"width: 45px; height: auto; margin-top: 5px;\">\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width: 68%; float: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px;\">[smartslider3 slider=2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width: 24%; background-color: white; float: left; text-align: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" height: 100px; background-color: pink;\">\r\n<center><img style=\"margin-top: 35px; width: 80%; height: auto;\" src=\"http://ttents-sample.at